export RT-AC85U := IPV6SUPP=y HTTPS=y MIPS32=r2 RALINK=y MT7621=y 
  BBEXTRAS=y USBEXTRAS=y EBTABLES=y SAMBA3=y MEDIASRV=y RTAC85U=y 
  MODEMPIN=y PARENTAL2=y ACCEL_PPTPD=y PRINTER=y USB="USB" MODEM=y 
  APP="network" AUTODICT=y LANWAN_LED=y BUILD_NAME="RT-AC85U" SHP=y 
  ODMPID=y DUAL_TRX=y LED_ALL=y NEW_RGDM=y RA_SKU_IN_DRV=y VPNC=y 
  OPENVPN=y DUMP_OOPS_MSG=y DEBUGFS=y REBOOT_SCHEDULE=y \
	WEBDAV=y CLOUDSYNC=y SWEBDAVCLIENT=y DROPBOXCLIENT=y 
        FTPCLIENT=y SAMBACLIENT=y SSH=y \
	NTFS="tuxera" HFS="tuxera" DISK_MONITOR=y \
	TIMEMACHINE=y MDNS=y EMAIL=y \
	ATED122=y \
	XHCI=y ATEUSB3_FORCE=y \
	BLINK_LED=y BTN_WPS_ALLLED=y \
	BOOT_FLASH_TYPE=NAND MTK_NAND=y \
	DRAM=128M \
	FIRST_IF=MT7615E SECOND_IF=MT7615E RALINK_DFS=y \
	QAM256_2G=y MUMIMO_5G=y UBI=y UBIFS=y PSISTLOG=y \
	TEMPROOTFS=y WPSMULTIBAND=y NEW_USER_LOW_RSSI=y \
	NEWSSID_REV2=y GETREALIP=y ATCOVER=y LAN50=y \
	EXTRA_KERNEL_CONFIGS="MT7621_BAUDRATE=57600 
        RT2880_DRAM_128M=y UBOOT_CMDLINE=y MODEL_RTAC85U=y 
        SMART_CARRIER_SENSE_SUPPORT=y MT_DFS_SUPPORT=y 
        DUAL_TRX=y FIRST_IF_IPAELNA=y SECOND_IF_IPAELNA=y"

export RT-AC85U_BASE := IPV6SUPP=y HTTPS=y MIPS32=r2 RALINK=y MT7621=y 
  BBEXTRAS=y USBEXTRAS=y EBTABLES=y SAMBA3=y MEDIASRV=y PARENTAL2=y 
  ACCEL_PPTPD=y  USB="USB"  AUTODICT=y LANWAN_LED=y SHP=y RTAC85U=y 
  ODMPID=y DUAL_TRX=y LED_ALL=y NEW_RGDM=y RA_SKU_IN_DRV=y OPENVPN=y 
  VPNC=y DUMP_OOPS_MSG=y DEBUGFS=y BWDPI=y REBOOT_SCHEDULE=y SSH=y \
    NTFS="tuxera" EXT4FS=y DISK_MONITOR=y MDNS=y EMAIL=y SYSSTATE=y 
      USB_SWAP=y \
    ATED122=y MTK_8021X3000=y \
    XHCI=y ATEUSB3_FORCE=y \
    BLINK_LED=y BTN_WPS_ALLLED=y \
    BOOT_FLASH_TYPE=NAND MTK_NAND=y \
    DRAM=128M \
    FIRST_IF=MT7615E SECOND_IF=MT7615E RALINK_DFS=y MTK_MUMIMO=y 
      MUMIMO_5G=y QAM256_2G=y \
    UBI=y UBIFS=y PSISTLOG=y \
    TEMPROOTFS=y WPSMULTIBAND=y \
    NEW_USER_LOW_RSSI=y NEWSSID_REV2=y GETREALIP=y ATCOVER=y LAN50=y

export RT-AC85U := $(RT-AC85U_BASE) HFS="tuxera"
export RT-AC85U += BUILD_NAME="RT-AC85U" 
  EXTRA_KERNEL_CONFIGS="MT7621_BAUDRATE=57600 RT2880_DRAM_128M=y 
  UBOOT_CMDLINE=y MODEL_RTAC85U=y SMART_CARRIER_SENSE_SUPPORT=y 
  MT_DFS_SUPPORT=y DUAL_TRX=y FIRST_IF_IPAELNA=y SECOND_IF_IPAELNA=y"
export RT-AC85U += MODEM=y PRINTER=y APP="network" WEBDAV=y 
  SMARTSYNCBASE=y TIMEMACHINE=y

export RT-AC65U := $(RT-AC85U_BASE)
export RT-AC65U += BASE_MODEL="RT-AC85U" BUILD_NAME="RT-AC65U" 
  EXTRA_KERNEL_CONFIGS="MT7621_BAUDRATE=57600 RT2880_DRAM_128M=y 
  UBOOT_CMDLINE=y MODEL_RTAC65U=y RTAC65U=y SMART_CARRIER_SENSE_SUPPORT=y 
  MT_DFS_SUPPORT=y DUAL_TRX=y FIRST_IF_IPAELNA=y SECOND_IF_IPAELNA=y"
export RT-AC65U += APP="none" NO_FTP=y
